                        <summary><p>Saptaṛṣīśvara temple, Lālkuṭi, Lālkuṭi taluk, Trichy district; on the north wall of the avant-corps (<foreign>ardha-maṇḍapa</foreign>). K.V. Subrahmanya Aiyer (EI 20.3, p. 51) and A.S. Ramanatha Ayyar (SII 14.12B, p. 9) assign it to 816 CE. However, later K.G. Krishnan (IEP 42) proposes the more convincing date of 6th December 875. This inscription is located below EI 20.3a (<ref target="DHARMA_INSPandya00012A"/>) and above SII 12.61.</p>
                            
